init = async (form, data) => { loadCurrentUserInformation().then((currentUser) => { data.currentUser = currentUser; form.triggerRedraw(); }); if (data.processVariables.recipient) { loadUserInformation(data.processVariables.recipient).then((user) => { data.recipient = user; form.triggerRedraw(); }); } if (data.processVariables.dv_initiator) { loadUserInformation(data.processVariables.dv_initiator).then((user) => { data.initiator = user; form.triggerRedraw(); }); } if (data.processVariables.step == 'results') { var decision = []; for (var i = 0; i < data.processVariables.decisions.length; i++) { var user = await loadUserInformation(data.processVariables.recipients[i]); decision.push({ decision: data.processVariables.decisions[i], recipient: user, comment: data.processVariables.comments[i] }) } form.getComponent('decisions').setValue(decision); } } function sendRequest(form, data) { var recipients = []; for (var i = 0; i < data.decisionMaker.length; i++) { console.log(data.decisionMaker[i]); if (data.decisionMaker[i].userName) { recipients.push("identity:///identityprovider/scim/users/" + data.decisionMaker[i].id); } else { recipients.push("identity:///identityprovider/scim/groups/" + data.decisionMaker[i].id); } } startProcess('get_decisions', { "variables": { "recipients": recipients, "request": data.request } }).then(() => { alert('request started'); window.history.back(); }) } const loadCurrentUserInformation = async () => { const response = await fetch("/identityprovider/validate", { method: 'GET', headers: { 'Cache-Control': 'no-cache', 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'origin': window.location.origin } }); const status = response.status; if (status < 200 || status > 299) { throw new Error(`Unable to fetch HAL JSON from server. Received status ${status}`, response); } return response.json(); }; const loadUserInformation = async (identity) => { const response = await fetch(identity.substring('11'), { method: 'GET', headers: { 'Cache-Control': 'no-cache', 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'origin': window.location.origin } }); const status = response.status; if (status < 200 || status > 299) { throw new Error(`Unable to fetch HAL JSON from server. Received status ${status}`, response); } return response.json(); } /* Start Process */ const startProcess = async (processId, data) => { console.log("Start process"); const response = await fetch("/process/processes/" + processId + "/instances", { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Cache-Control': 'no-cache', 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'origin': window.location.origin }, body: JSON.stringify(data) }); const status = response.status; if (status < 200 || status > 299) { throw new Error(`Unable to fetch HAL JSON from server. Received status ${status}`, response); } return status; };"}
